- Top riders are defined as those who are ranked 1st, 2nd, or 3rd in their respective categories based on average speed; 
- Completed races refer to races with a status of 'Completed';
- Average speed refers to the speed of the rider during the race, measured in km/h;
- Total training distance refers to the cumulative distance covered by each rider during their training sessions, as recorded in the analytics data.

sql:
SELECT race_date
FROM races
ORDER BY race_date ASC;
